ovider is unavailable\"));\n    }\n\n    @SuppressWarnings(\"unchecked\")\n    private static Class<FileSystemProvider> fileSystemProviderType(FileSystemProvider provider) {\n        return (Class<FileSystemProvider>) provider.getClass();\n    }\n}\n"}
