ader)` at `ModuleHandler.java:143`\n\nThe test accepts the expected module-system failure after that point and still handles Native Image unsupported dynamic class loading via `NativeImageSupport`.\n\nI did not run tests.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0834da44b1b700280169f974b01c1481a1ad46ebfa762772e4\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1432, "output": 1260, "cacheRead": 56832, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 59524, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1777956000551, "responseId": "resp_0834da44b1b700280169f974a1244481a188a50da693cca07f"}, "toolResults": []}
